OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1777932664
OL,3,CBomb hoax suspect at Peter Kay show
OL,4,Cremanded in custody
OL,6,FA 19-year-old charged over an alleged
OL,7,Fbomb hoax which forced a Peter Kay
OL,8,Fcomedy show to be evacuated has been
OL,9,Fremanded in custody until next month.
OL,11,FOmar Majed appeared at Birmingham
OL,12,FMagistrates' Court on Monday (4 May),
OL,13,Fwith charges alleging that he
OL,14,Fcommunicated to a police officer and
OL,15,Fothers information, which he knew or
OL,16,Fbelieved to be false, that a bomb was
OL,17,Fpresent in the arena.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
