FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1777932664
OL,3,CBomb hoax suspect at Peter Kay show
OL,4,Cremanded in custody
OL,6,FThe court was told thousands of fans
OL,7,Fhad to be evacuated after the teenager
OL,8,Fallegedly "barged" his way into
OL,9,FBirmingham's Utilita Arena without a
OL,10,Fticket.
OL,12,FProsecutor Ros Buttler told the court
OL,13,FMajed was alleged to have indicated to
OL,14,Fa police constable and others that a
OL,15,Fbomb may have been left at the venue.
OL,17,FThe alleged hoax had "serious
OL,18,Frepercussions" at an event with an
OL,19,Fexpected crowd of almost 13,000
OL,20,Fpeople, she added.
OL,26,@pD@KOUpD@RO]yD@VOUzD@NO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1777932664
OL,3,CBomb hoax suspect at Peter Kay show
OL,4,Cremanded in custody
OL,6,FMajed, of Graham Road, Saltley,
OL,7,FBirmingham, gave no indication of plea
OL,8,Fto a single charge of communicating
OL,9,Ffalse information to police contrary
OL,10,Fto the Criminal Law Act.
OL,12,FDistrict Judge Smith also refused a
OL,13,Fbail application.
OL,15,FShe said: "Based on everything I have
OL,16,Fread and have heard I am satisfied
OL,17,Fthat the case should be dealt with in
OL,18,Fthe Crown Court.
OL,20,F"The case will be sent to Birmingham
OL,21,FCrown Court on 1 June."
OL,26,@wD@KOU|D@AOU}D@WO]
