OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1777932664
OL,3,CBomb hoax suspect at Peter Kay show
OL,4,Cremanded in custody
OL,6,FKay, 52, was ushered off stage during
OL,7,Fhis show at the Utilita Arena on
OL,8,FFriday.
OL,10,FThe show was cancelled after the
OL,11,Fevacuation and West Midlands Police
OL,12,Flater said "nothing suspicious was
OL,13,Ffound" during searches.
OL,15,FOn Saturday evening, the force said:
OL,16,F"An evacuation of the arena was
OL,17,Fordered yesterday evening after a
OL,18,Freport of a suspicious bag being left
OL,19,Fin the area.
OL,26,@tD@LOUuD@FO]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
