PN,37405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1777932664
OL,3,CBomb hoax suspect at Peter Kay show
OL,4,Cremanded in custody
OL,6,F"Following searches, nothing
OL,7,Fsuspicious was found and we are
OL,8,Fgrateful to everyone for their co-
OL,9,Foperation and understanding.
OL,11,F"As always our priority is the safety
OL,12,Fof the public."
OL,14,FThe show was part of Kay's Better Late
OL,15,FThan Never national tour, which will
OL,16,Fsee all proceeds donated to 12 cancer
OL,17,Fcharities.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUtD@OO]
